These frontmatter lines are ignored by the parser (not title: or author:).
This file deliberately triggers every error and note type the parser emits.
Rename to .ttale after download. Run once plain, once with -w to see notes.

Title: Parser Stress Test
Author: Test Harness

Scene: Start

A clean starting scene. This should produce no errors or notes.

Choices:
- Continue on -> Good Ending

---

Scene: Good Ending

A clean ending scene. No errors or notes expected here.

THE END

---

Scene: Dup Choices

This scene declares two Choices sections. The second one should be merged
into the first and flagged as a note.

Choices:
- First choice -> Good Ending
- Second choice -> Good Ending

Choices:
- Third choice -> Good Ending

---

Scene: Inline Added

This scene puts a real-looking choice on the same line as the Choices keyword.

Choices: - Inline choice -> Good Ending

